      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my car. It has been such a reliable companion and is still in really wonderful shape! It's been well-loved and looked after, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with its next owner immediately. It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable ride without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019d love for it to go to a good home, so feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come see it in person!",
