    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 1993 Mazda RX-7 FD features the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary engine, delivering linear power through the entire RPM range. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise 5-speed manual transmission and a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. Recent maintenance includes a compression test with healthy results across all faces, an upgraded aluminum multi-core radiator to manage thermal loads, and a simplified vacuum line rack to ensure boost stability. The chassis remains rigid with its original double-wishbone suspension geometry and four-piston front calipers. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the mechanical integrity and kinematic performance are dialed in for the purist driver.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
