    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a fantastic opportunity for a buyer seeking a dependable and aesthetically pleasing ride. The exterior paint retains a deep, impressive shine, showing only the minor, inevitable signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin has been kept in excellent shape; the upholstery is free of tears, the dashboard remains crack-free, and every electronic component\u2014from the infotainment system to the climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, it has been treated with the utmost care, boasting a documented history of regular oil changes and a recent comprehensive inspection that included new brake pads and a tire rotation. It starts up immediately, shifts smoothly through all gears, and provides a quiet, comfortable driving experience. This car is truly ready for its next owner to drive away with confidence.",
